      <section id="details">
        <h2 class="gem-c-heading gem-c-heading--font-size-27 gem-c-heading--mobile-top-margin  ">Details</h2>


        
<div class="gem-c-govspeak govuk-govspeak direction-ltr" data-module="govspeak">
      <div class="govspeak">
<p>This guidance is designed to help people planning to get married or form a civil partnership in England, and assist venues to prepare for small ceremonies, receptions and celebrations to take place.</p>
</div>
</div>

      </section>
    </div>

    <div class="app-c-published-dates app-c-published-dates--history" id="history" data-module="toggle" lang="en">
    Published 29 June 2020
    <br></br>Last updated 14 October 2020
      <a href="#full-history" class="app-c-published-dates__toggle govuk-link" data-controls="full-history" data-expanded="false" data-toggled-text="- hide all updates">+ show all updates</a>
      <div class="app-c-published-dates__change-history js-hidden" id="full-history">
        <ol>
            <li class="app-c-published-dates__change-item">
              <time class="app-c-published-dates__change-date timestamp" datetime="2020-10-14T12:43:45.000+01:00">14 October 2020</time>
              <p class="app-c-published-dates__change-note">Guidance updated to incorporate changes in regulations, as they affect weddings and civil partnerships, announced by the Prime Minister on 12 October 2020.</p>
            </li>
            <li class="app-c-published-dates__change-item">
              <time class="app-c-published-dates__change-date timestamp" datetime="2020-10-07T14:23:34.000+01:00">7 October 2020</time>
              <p class="app-c-published-dates__change-note">Updated guidance on wedding and civil partnership receptions and celebrations. Changes cover the rules on face coverings, distance between tables, singing in groups of more than 6, dancing, music volume and enforcement.</p>
            </li>
            <li class="app-c-published-dates__change-item">
              <time class="app-c-published-dates__change-date timestamp" datetime="2020-09-26T15:07:37.000+01:00">26 September 2020</time>
              <p class="app-c-published-dates__change-note">Updated guidance on number of guests allowed, legal requirements for businesses to be closed between 10pm and 5am and supporting staff to self-isolate, mandatory face coverings for staff, mandatory table service at licenced venues, new NHS Test and Trace QR code and guests prohibited from joining in with performances.</p>
            </li>
            <li class="app-c-published-dates__change-item">
              <time class="app-c-published-dates__change-date timestamp" datetime="2020-09-24T10:35:24.000+01:00">24 September 2020</time>
              <p class="app-c-published-dates__change-note">Guidance updated to incorporate changes in regulations, as they affect marriages and civil partnerships, announced by the Prime Minister on 22 September 2020.</p>
            </li>
            <li class="app-c-published-dates__change-item">
              <time class="app-c-published-dates__change-date timestamp" datetime="2020-09-11T19:22:47.000+01:00">11 September 2020</time>
              <p class="app-c-published-dates__change-note">Updated guidance on maintaining social distancing between different households and mandatory test and trace requirements.</p>
            </li>
            <li class="app-c-published-dates__change-item">
              <time class="app-c-published-dates__change-date timestamp" datetime="2020-08-14T16:24:57.000+01:00">14 August 2020</time>
              <p class="app-c-published-dates__change-note">Updated to take account of changes in guidance on singing and playing brass and wind instruments in front of an audience and on holding small wedding receptions.</p>
            </li>
            <li class="app-c-published-dates__change-item">
              <time class="app-c-published-dates__change-date timestamp" datetime="2020-08-13T22:35:12.000+01:00">13 August 2020</time>
              <p class="app-c-published-dates__change-note">Added guidance on receptions and celebrations.</p>
            </li>
            <li class="app-c-published-dates__change-item">
              <time class="app-c-published-dates__change-date timestamp" datetime="2020-08-04T17:17:22.000+01:00">4 August 2020</time>
              <p class="app-c-published-dates__change-note">Amended in line with the Prime Minister's statement on 31 July.</p>
            </li>
            <li class="app-c-published-dates__change-item">
              <time class="app-c-published-dates__change-date timestamp" datetime="2020-08-03T09:48:39.000+01:00">3 August 2020</time>
              <p class="app-c-published-dates__change-note">Updated to reflect additional requirements on face coverings. Amendments to the roadmap for wedding receptions.</p>
            </li>
            <li class="app-c-published-dates__change-item">
              <time class="app-c-published-dates__change-date timestamp" datetime="2020-07-17T19:11:15.000+01:00">17 July 2020</time>
              <p class="app-c-published-dates__change-note">Amended to show that from 1 August, small wedding receptions will be able to take place - this means sit-down meals for no more than 30 people, subject to COVID-19 Secure guidance.</p>
            </li>
            <li class="app-c-published-dates__change-item">
              <time class="app-c-published-dates__change-date timestamp" datetime="2020-07-04T07:09:24.000+01:00">4 July 2020</time>
              <p class="app-c-published-dates__change-note">Guidance updated.</p>
            </li>
            <li class="app-c-published-dates__change-item">
              <time class="app-c-published-dates__change-date timestamp" datetime="2020-06-29T00:39:00.000+01:00">29 June 2020</time>
              <p class="app-c-published-dates__change-note">First published.</p>
            </li>
        </ol>
      </div>
</div>

